{"tid":2400500,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"澳門行政長官賀一誠率官員接種國藥疫苗","createTime":"2021-02-09T04:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T07:21:17.000Z","uid":362414,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5aaf5aa2a1ece52ad9189fe960eebaaa1cfdec04","tid":2400500,"uid":362414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T04:11:09.000Z","msg":"澳門今日起安排三類人士優先免費接種新冠疫苗，澳門行政長官賀一誠早上率領一眾官員接種。<br />\n<br />\n澳門早上舉行新冠疫苗接種啟動儀式，澳門行政長官賀一誠首先接種疫苗 ，之後澳門經濟財政司司長李偉農、保安司司長黃少澤、社會文化司、運輸工務司、海關關長等官員陸續接種。<br />\n<br />\n十萬劑國藥疫苗早前運抵澳門，當地首階段會為醫護、警員、學校教職員等，暴露風險較高人士接種；二階段開放給全澳門居民，最早在今個月22日後接種。<br />\n<br />\n當局已與一間保險公司簽約，<strong><span class=\"red\">如因接種疫苗三個月內，出現不良反應導致死亡或完全及永久傷殘，每人最高可獲一百萬賠償。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=423503\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D423503&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=f60c8ec2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D423503&h=ae55183f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=423503</a>"},{"pid":"587d9ce19bd0c652f3a2856fdf2174e6e33add07","tid":2400500,"uid":274149,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T04:13:18.000Z","msg":"呢啲就叫有誠意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d30f9007a49d5e643374d14912af085e29986ef","tid":2400500,"uid":178039,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"澳門扮都扮得好好多<br />\n垃圾777又驚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796b306085e65445aaf7904bf28bb3a65beba580","tid":2400500,"uid":86246,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T04:14:43.000Z","msg":"點解賀一誠做得好過林鄭咁多<br />\n又係澳門有香港冇"},{"pid":"ea502481a75287b1ff4697b712d0c0968cb1d828","tid":2400500,"uid":357803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote